{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Face your worst school nightmares with nothing but paper airplanes! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into gameplay set in an exaggerated school setting. Along the way, you\u2019ll encounter a variety of enemies, each with their own strengths and weaknesses. Besides defeating them, you\u2019ll also need to focus on collecting the pocket money they drop, which you can spend at the school store. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/School_Store.gif?t=1738011842\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Between levels, you can buy new items, choose your school persona, and upgrade your paper airplanes \u2014 every decision could be crucial to your success in later stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/Perks.png?t=1738011842\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Besides the standard enemies, you\u2019ll face bosses that embody your most dreaded school fears!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During the boss fights, each one enters a unique rage mode, adding an extra challenge to the battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/Bosses.gif?t=1738011842\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Bully","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3217440/737ae8f2247ff1142775e26ca0e6f1d7f9eb4b3b.jpg"},{"name":"Dietitian","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3217440/2117a6830e1609564a481c9ec0683a83b9213947.jpg"},{"name":"School Terror","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3217